  "body": "The kubernetes tests have this:\r\n~~~\r\n\t// Work-around for timing condition that results in no-data being returned in test environment.\r\n\ttime.Sleep(3 * time.Second)\r\n~~~\r\nWhich means that even in our code we need a workaround. This should be replaced with either a call to a blocking channel that gets closed once we've fully started or something else.\r\n\r\nThis is also needed for #985",
